        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Driver Fatigue Prevention Act</b></p> <p>This bill amends the Fair Labor Standards Act of 1938 to make over-the-road bus drivers subject to limitations on the maximum number of hours that an employee may work under such Act.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
